## Naming Decision Tree

### For Files

```
Is it a...
├─ Model? → singular snake_case (user.rb)
├─ Controller? → plural snake_case + _controller (users_controller.rb)
├─ View? → action name (index.html.erb) or partial (_form.html.erb)
├─ Job? → singular snake_case + _job (notification_job.rb)
├─ Channel? → singular/plural snake_case + _channel (comments_channel.rb)
├─ Mailer? → singular snake_case + _mailer (user_mailer.rb)
├─ Test? → matches class + _test (user_test.rb)
└─ JavaScript? → snake_case + _controller (dropdown_controller.js)
```

### For Variables/Methods

```
Is it...
├─ Ruby?
│  ├─ Variable? → snake_case (user_name)
│  ├─ Method? → snake_case (calculate_total)
│  ├─ Constant? → SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE (MAX_ATTEMPTS)
│  ├─ Boolean method? → ends with ? (active?)
│  └─ Bang method? → ends with ! (save!)
└─ JavaScript?
   ├─ Variable? → camelCase (userName)
   ├─ Function? → camelCase (calculateTotal)
   ├─ Constant? → SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE (MAX_ATTEMPTS)
   └─ Class? → PascalCase (ArticleManager)
```
